originalText.text: So much to say in such a little box! I came to Melissa during a time I needed healing with my past, present, and wanting setting up a solid future. She’s helped me connect to my spiritual side and bring out a part of softness in me I didn’t even know existed after so many years hiding under a tough exterior. She’s super reasonably priced and i genuinely look forward to our sessions.

originalText.text: I have been working with Melissa since the Spring of 2022 and from the first day I was introduced to her at one of her events, I knew that she was exactly the support I needed. During our coaching sessions, Melissa makes me feel seen, safe, supported and challenged. I have grown so much in the past 6 months of working with her and I can’t wait to see what we continue to do together. I highly recommend Melissa’s services to those that are ready to receive them. Thank you so much for all of the love and support that you provide beyond our coaching sessions. Melissa is not only a coach, she she is a healer, a community builder and so much more. I am beyond grateful for you.

originalText.text:
I’m so happy a friend of mine told me about Melissa. After just 8 sessions I saw and felt myself and my life beautifully blossoming. I’ve had different types of therapist over the last 10 - 12 years. And truthfully I love them all, they have all done what was needed for me at the time, BUT Melissa, she really brings out the core in you, sometimes it’s unbelievable the energy and emotions you have, that all you need is a little guidance.
I started with Melissa for some  personal and just general life stuff/ advice and guidance* and what I’ve gotten so far is way more then expected, wayyyyyyyy more.
Her professionalism and creative thinking really makes you want so much more for yourself.
Shes 10/10- I couldn’t be more happy to have someone like her in my life.
Thank you!

originalText.text:
I have had the honor of being one of Melissa's clients over the last 2 years. Before meeting her, I was always apprehensive about Life Coaching and letting anyone too close to even assist with my emotional growth. However her professionalism, spiritual profoundness, ability to communicate the truth and encourage her clients growth in the process is something I've never experienced before. Presently, I could say that I've become more balanced in both personal and career because of her mindset, methods, and approach.
She's patient, she's kind, she's REAL, she's strong and teaches others to tap into the light in them. Needless to say, I highly recommend this phenomenal force!
With Melissa, you will gain more than a "session",
you will gain a new life of abundance!!

originalText.text: I met Melissa a few weeks ago at an incredible sister circle. I had opened up about something personal and immediately Melissa was already in tune with me. That very day I went up to her and spoke to her about my interest in receiving spiritual and mental guidance. I've been searching for the right therapist for so long, I am truly blessed to have run into Melissa. She is professional in the best way and her spiritual guidance is so necessary. Her ability to connect empathetically is incredible, her vibe is welcoming and full of grace, you honestly end up feeling graceful too just being in her presence or speaking to her. I've been speaking to her for 2 weeks now and have joined her amazing Pep Talks. I literally feel the change happening within me, I am in a much brighter place than I was when I first met Melissa. As she would say "things are happening!" I am so grateful to have her as a guide on this mysterious, unpredictable, and yet beautiful life. Thank you Muse!
